f Schematic Diagram. Interpret the given Schematic Diagram by drawing and connecting its Pictorial Diagram.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,70,0,1,0,NULL,3,1,0,0,'2026-03-31 19:40:57','2026-03-31 19:40:57',NULL);
